      loadingTips: !<string[]>
        - Asking the Witch where the restroom is
        - Spawning suspicious book stacks
        - Spawning random room furniture
        - "Finding out if it's October 31st"
        - Researching if vampires are real
        - Placing unfavourable cobwebs
        - Placing unfavourable cobwebs
        - Feeding the ghost in the basement (again)
        - Calibrating the screams to surround sound
        - Whispering secret hints to the walls
        - Hiding the spare key where you’ll never find it
        - Asking the mirror who’s the most trapped of them all
        - Counting how many eyes are watching you right now
        - Shuffling clues for maximum confusion
        - Asking the painting to stop following you
        - Verifying all puzzles are technically solvable
        - Spawning additional chills down your spine
        - Rewiring the chandelier to flicker just right
        - Writing new cryptic notes in suspicious handwriting
        - Updating escape difficulty to “questionable”
        - Hiring a new narrator who doesn’t whisper so much
        - Patching hole in reality (temporary fix)
        - Checking if anyone escaped yet... yeah no
        - Reprogramming doors to sound more mysterious
